N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 86.16 - Money gifts prohibited

State Regulations

No manufacturer or wholesaler shall give or promise, directly or indirectly, to any retailer any fee, gratuity, rebate, credit or
discount of any nature whatsoever for any gift or service enumerated in this
